{
  "stem": "10699.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we were all in the barracks there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "From the 17th, we were there-- I write the date here-- till the 26th of May.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, it was-- the 17th of May was a beautiful day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had made arrangements for some friends to go to the countryside with our bicycles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was Ascension Day in France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were all looking forward to get away from Saint-Etienne.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was the day we were all arrested.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the sad part was, as it was getting so dangerous, my mother had found the week before in a convent in Le Puy, they were going to, to take us in.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, it was a matter of days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were now frightened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was only one thing to do-- is to leave Saint-Etienne.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were leaving in a few days' time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In the cellar, we had a reserve of food, you know, eggs, and potatoes, and everything, in case we couldn't go out anymore.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, the situation was now bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were ready to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The sad part, the unfortunate part was that my mother was that day with the wine merchant.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were looking for the Hungarian family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was so unlucky and so tragic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my poor mother, you know, she couldn't forgive herself [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that she happened to be there at that very moment.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] By then-- by now we were all together in that-- in that-- in that barracks, army barracks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And on the 26th, when they took us, we were now a whole train of Jewish people-- families.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They took us to the station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The Gestapo [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] chief came over to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
